[div class=p 
	"This TAS has heavy glitch abuse. For those who aren't familiar with it, this hack can be completed without any glitch, and there are two bad endings if Mario hasn't rescued Luigi.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=MinorDetails 
	" Minor Details
	$LF
]h4
[ul 
	[li 
		" In the first underground room, I entered the pipe a few frames later on purpose, to save frames during the damage clip in the next room.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" I've also thought of and tested other solutions in the Bullet Bill room, but this is the best I can get. The Bullet Bill used is frame precise.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" In the Luigi room, the wall clipping isn't for entertainment; it saves 2 frames.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" Before the flagpole, I performed music sync with jumping.
		$LF
	]li
